FAQs
What programs does Humanitas University offer?
Humanitas University offers a range of undergraduate and graduate programs, including Medicine and Surgery, Nursing, Medical Biotechnology, and Medical Informatics.

How can I apply to Humanitas University Italy?
You can apply by completing the online application form on the university’s website and submitting the required documents, such as academic transcripts and letters of recommendation.

What financial aid options are available?
The university offers merit-based and need-based scholarships to help students finance their education.

What support is available for international students?
International students receive support through orientation programs, language courses, and assistance with visa applications and immigration matters.
